1. Parse Input
  a. Map input.lines
    i. split lines by " "
    ii. direction on left side
    iii. movement amount on right side
  b. starting at (0, 0), move head {amount} spaces in {direction}
  c. determine tail position using provided logic
    i. head and tail must always be touching
    ii. if head is ever two steps directly up, down, left, or right
        from the tail, the tail must also move one step in that direction
    iii. if head & tail aren't touching, and aren't in the same row
         and column, the tail always moves one step diagonally to keep up
         